sequenceDiagram
    participant O as 编排控制
    participant G as 治理层
    participant R as 知识检索
    participant P as 推理内核
    O->>G: subject + query + resource scope
    G-->>O: allowed filters / deny
    O->>R: query + enforced filters
    R-->>O: document/version/content/chunk + locator + ACL
    O->>P: instructions + allowlisted evidence IDs / locators
    P-->>O: atomic claims + citation refs + uncertainty
    O->>G: verify validity / correctness / completeness
    G->>G: Citation syntax + semantic support + current ACL
    G->>G: 使用点复核 / 流式段提交 / conflict
    G-->>O: allow / redact / abstain
